          body: '长沙简牍博物馆 makes old Changsha administrative rather than mythical: household registers, tax, law, correspondence, and excavation context become the texture of a real city. Its regular closure is Tuesday, unlike the Monday pattern at many museums, and its current display upgrade makes the newest notice important. Continue on foot through a bounded part of Tianxin rather than trying to cover every “old street.” End at 杜甫江阁 only if the current ticketed interior or evening program adds value; otherwise the public east-bank promenade carries the river view for free.',
